        <body>
            *in css there are 2 types of transforms 
        one 2d transform and other is 3d transform
        *in transform we have different properties like :
        -rotate(in these we can use angle or we can mention turn(.25 turn means 90 degree))
        we can mention rotatex,y,z, it is with respective axis
        -scale-like rotate properties we can apply to scale properties          
        -skew
